&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;In this role, you will break down complex requirements into structured, actionable tasks. As part of the Data Services department, you will collaborate with a global team of data engineers, data analysts, and other big data specialists across the organisation.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
