&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;At least 3 years of hands-on experience in commercial Software Engineering roles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good experience working with front-end code, ideally using Angular.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Extensive experience in developing cloud software using:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;AWS services - Lambda, ECS, DynamoDB, Opensearch&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Terraform for writing Infrastructure as Code scripts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Typescript&lt;/li&gt;
