&lt;li&gt;Evaluate CPA, CPC, and hybrid performance models for risk exposure and abuse potential.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor lifecycle and behavioral signals across publisher activity to proactively identify risks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with internal stakeholders to assess onboarding and ongoing publisher quality.&lt;/li&gt;
